          <div id="review_8525286_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  正如蒙曼老师所说,唐朝是个开放的时代，当时的中国还没有被程朱理学所影响。再加上之前几百年的胡华融合,都为中国历史上这个红妆时代做了铺垫。武则天能登上权利顶峰，成为一代女皇，有她自己的努力，也有其他诸多客观因素。正如蒙曼老师引用黑格尔的名言：所有伟大的历史事件...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8525286_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8525286_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3047736">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3047736/" class="title-link">武则天后期的动乱时期</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3047736"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/31448552/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/31448552/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">林花谢了春红</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-03-07"
      class="main-meta">2010-03-07 21:40:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3047736_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这部书讲述了武则天后期到玄宗开元盛世这段八九年的动乱历史，太平公主、韦皇后、安乐公主、上官婉儿四个女人相继登上权力的巅峰，争夺最高权力。但是她们都失败了。这部书就是讲的这段历史。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3047736_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3047736_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










